{"tid":1267012,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要做自了漢, 不要讓中共笑到最後。","createTime":"2019-06-29T16:57:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-04T00:24:36.000Z","uid":54785,"like":24,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dd0b3a4baaf4b4dce270ca279afdbd41dc6d4718","tid":1267012,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:57:20.000Z","msg":"女烈士請安息, 你的心意大家都收到了。<br />\n<br />\n但對不起, 我一定不會跟隨你的腳步, 我也會指責所有打算跟隨你腳步的人。<br />\n<br />\n我們希望向所有烈士發出最高的敬意, 而我們能對你發出最高的敬意就是, 承諾你會是最後一個犧牲者。這令你的犧牲變得更有意義。<br />\n<br />\n烈士們的任務已經完成。如果再有人打算以這方式離開我們, 就只是一種自私。我不但不會向你致敬, 而且我會公開指責你。因為你是一名為求解脫, 而把重擔留給其他人的自了漢。你是叛徒。我不管你有多難捱, 請跟我們一起捱下去。最後的勝利屬於我們。<br />\n<br />\n烈士的願望不可能是希望有其他人需要跟隨他們的腳步, 不可能希望中共會因為我們所有人都犧牲掉而笑到最後。他們用生命作代價, 是希望喚醒我們, 希望提醒我們要繼續抗爭, 不要因為挫折而放棄。提醒了我們, 自由的代價, 可以很昂貴, 卻值得。<br />\n<br />\n請你, 我們珍而重之的每一個香港人, 好好活下去。<br />\n<br />\n不要做自了漢, 不要讓中共笑到最後。"},{"pid":"91d33ea8a0fe8b482e153241c72f00d5ec020153","tid":1267012,"uid":236917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n好心痛"},{"pid":"22d1ae73fc4ae5cdb93713a6620772fa123177d1","tid":1267012,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91d33ea8a0fe8b482e153241c72f00d5ec020153","tid":1267012,"uid":236917,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T16:59:52.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n好心痛"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:05:24.000Z","msg":"共勉之"},{"pid":"28e32532dd649e8a8e5ab93a3fb34bc6c5b2fb00","tid":1267012,"uid":245033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"心痛烈士 希望唔會再出現下一位<br />\n因為一單自殺都嫌多<br />\n亦唔想有人為左叫醒更多人而自行了斷"},{"pid":"d91fbd628bf437e73836b69c1d51b6720b23d325","tid":1267012,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"28e32532dd649e8a8e5ab93a3fb34bc6c5b2fb00","tid":1267012,"uid":245033,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:10:18.000Z","msg":"心痛烈士 希望唔會再出現下一位<br />\n因為一單自殺都嫌多<br />\n亦唔想有人為左叫醒更多人而自行了斷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T17:55:13.000Z","msg":"希望係最後一次"},{"pid":"c705ca8110f1b335d834247b43fc9d1502d9ac5c","tid":1267012,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:17:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf1dfacd9ecc9b94f3f367271aee58ed97fa55b","tid":1267012,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:25:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J6ogywo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ6ogywo.png&h=a84d61c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"65ca85eb84a156cce3ab1e1ce040cc73eb18d7e6","tid":1267012,"uid":43082,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T18:32:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"11c3039d214ff2f3e1f3c6c76c8ec17844e6298d","tid":1267012,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T03:58:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f18e691b8e1ee2bceb7926f64b20f5a65bcf6945","tid":1267012,"uid":211347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"Push."},{"pid":"feb393d52452db2be84de0f5baef3ff5949d5f74","tid":1267012,"uid":47659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T04:01:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92123205c3e9e54268934ebc27e6ae34269f6c30","tid":1267012,"uid":54785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-04T00:24:36.000Z","msg":"我冇嘢講"}]}